Terrorsaur:






Terrorsaur circled the area in beast mode. There was a singe mark on 
his back where Rowdy Wolf had shot him robot mode. He had seen the 
last moments of a battle between his crewmates and a small groups of 
Maximals. He circled widely around to the Maximal's group, following 
them.
